        </tbody>
    </table>

    <p>A pack of 20 cigarettes puts roughly 240 mg of nicotine into your body (though only about 1–3 mg per cigarette is actually absorbed). One 8–10 mg pouch, kept in the mouth for 20–30 minutes, delivers comparable absorption without the harm.</p>

    <div style="background: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 16px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 24px 0;">
        <strong style="color: #856404;">Pro tip:</strong> If you're unsure, start at the lower end of your range. You can always increase strength later. It's better to have mild cravings in week one than to feel sick.
