    <p>Quitting smoking is hard. Nicotine pouches don't make it easy, but they do make it possible. By matching your strength, committing to a structured transition, and staying consistent, you can move from cigarettes to pouches in 4–6 weeks. From there, gradual reduction or long-term maintenance with minimal health risk becomes your choice.</p>

    <p>The best pouch is the one you'll use. Start today.</p>

